        <item>
            <title>Ray-Ban Meta 智能眼镜，加入 AI 功能美国率先提供</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/ray-ban-meta-ai-trial/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ray-ban-meta-ai-trial</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/ray-ban-meta-ai-trial/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 03:06:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Meta AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Ray-Ban Meta Smart Glasses]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210920</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今年 9 月于 Meta Connect 2023 发表的 Ray-Ban Meta 智能眼镜第二代，最近新增包括影像识别和文字翻译等人工智能相关功能，让这款眼镜不只是用作拍摄照片和影片的隐蔽相机镜头。Meta CEO 朱克伯格日前透过其社交平台，示范了部分用于 Ray-Ban Meta 智能眼镜的新功能。</p><p><span id="more-1210920"></span></p><p>透过 Meta AI 人工智能的协助，佩戴 Ray-Ban Meta 智能眼镜的用户只要看著一件恤衫，就可以利用语音查询适合配衬的裤子建议，亦可以望著照片再要求人工智能编写一段搞笑的文字描述。此外，Meta AI 更懂得辨认用户手上的物品种类，甚至将梗图上的外语翻译成英语。</p><p>根据朱克伯格的示范，Ray-Ban Meta 智能眼镜不会全时分析佩戴者周围环境，只会在用户说出「Hey Meta」时，人工智能助理才会启动。上述功能现在只向极少数参加了 Early Access Program 的美国 Ray-Ban Meta 智能眼镜用户试用，暂时未知功能正式推出的时间表。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_10938"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/V7CNcchh3Ts?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://themessenger.com/tech/meta-ray-ban-smart-glasses-ai-upgrade-features">themessenger</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/ray-ban-meta-ai-trial/ai/">Ray-Ban Meta 智能眼镜，加入 AI 功能美国率先提供</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
